[Maps of Nepal can be seen at https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nepalese_Federal_States and https://promedmail.org/promed-post?place=4603729,12918. Nepalgunj is a Sub-Metropolitan Municipality in Banke District, one of the 75 districts in Nepal; it is located in Province Five, in midwestern Nepal, near the southern border with Uttar Pradesh state of India (https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nepalgunj).

